            "inlineLink": false
          },
          "description": "<p><strong>Developer</strong></p><ul><li>Developed a real-time object classification system for automated sorting on a conveyor belt.</li><li>Collected and labeled image data, trained a YOLOv8 detection model, and integrated predictions with Arduino-controlled hardware.</li><li>Connected camera input, servo control, and computer vision inference for an end-to-end AI + IoT prototype.</li><li>Technologies: Python, YOLOv8, OpenCV, Arduino, C++.</li></ul>"
        }
